{"tid":1355390,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"無失過焦 無失過焦 咪撚再話失焦","createTime":"2019-07-23T09:52:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-23T15:39:56.000Z","uid":74954,"like":133,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"29028235ce83e29d0cbd74e999234f8e125cc304","tid":1355390,"uid":74954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T09:52:05.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>光復元朗唔係失焦</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n元朗單野係因為<span style=\"color: red;\">警察政府</span>有d野做唔到<br />\n所以只好靠黑社會出手/助力<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">想搞白色恐怖</span></strong></span><br />\n令到<span style=\"color: red;\">我地</span>唔敢再出街<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">唔敢再示威</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但係我地呢一次光復元朗係話俾佢地知<br />\n我地<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔怕白色恐怖</span></span><br />\n唔怕強權<br />\n如果唔光復  佢地利用黑社會既手段只會更嚴重<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n只要一日我地未死<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">我地無論係咩惡劣情況下都會堅持五大訴求</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">係元朗聚焦返５＋１大訴求</span><br />\n１。全面撤回送中<br />\n２。撤銷暴動定性<br />\n３。釋放被捕義士並承諾永不追究<br />\n４。全面實行雙普選<br />\n５。成立獨立調查委員會追究黑警責任＋徹查警黑勾結元朗暴動"},{"pid":"a92a54946a19e95977249dd50a7a4c3d468f214f","tid":1355390,"uid":74954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T09:54:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cde4f7831d9e25783eef0dfe1a7baf3aa4a8bd2b","tid":1355390,"uid":74954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T10:07:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f19e26c8c00a3451af0a1e83393cce6e750424a","tid":1355390,"uid":74954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T10:09:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea837ff90708d649fc6b1934351d4cfd19b133b7","tid":1355390,"uid":74954,"like":0,"disl